{"tid":1977011,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"限聚令完結代表d咩？","createTime":"2020-04-17T15:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T22:08:13.000Z","uid":197866,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1d39bb2c5cab3b2392b990c2de315324f6ef9fb5","tid":1977011,"uid":197866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:35:47.000Z","msg":"本港新增確診個案<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>連續6日</strong></span>維持單位數。<br />\n<br />\n我唔敢講香城抗疫成功，但香城之所以到而家仲未有大規模傳染，澄清番：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">柒婆絕對冇丁點兒功勞</span></span>，武漢肺炎由第一單到而家過千單，佢從來冇呼籲過<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全民戴口罩</span></span>，身為黃絲嘅大家人應該心知點解; 到而家都仲係要大家自己撲啲貴口罩酒精番嚟，自己救自己，理得市民死; 當年佢識用<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">緊急法禁止出街戴口罩</span></span>，武肺疫情又唔見佢會用緊急法禁止大家出街?淨係識邊度出事先禁嗰度做生意。貫徹攬炒之母一貫作風，冇樣嘢有貢獻，大家抗緊疫，佢成班on9就坐喺度睇sam hui。<br />\n<br />\n我想講，如果唔係2月<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">罷工醫護爭取到封大部分關</span></span>，守喺前線，喺防疫裝備緊拙嘅情況下對抗武肺，大家已經中撚哂招啦!<br />\n<br />\n大家係要多謝前線醫護，但唔係要拍手，唔係要杯麵，唔係要生果。而係要話比政權知道，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">we are still angry， 我哋依然毋忘初衷</span></span>。反送中好快就一年，五大訴求依然被無視; 鄧pk上場之後，黑警沒有最黑，只有更黑; 而家抗疫時期仲要專查黃店。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋其實冇。贏。過。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n本港新增確診個案連續6日維持單位數，呢個勢落去限聚令冇可能無限期繼續落去。大家係手足既，唔該做好準備，限聚限一完，唔該大家，住邊都好，用咩方式都好，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和勇不分回復番所有抗爭行動</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">商場唱歌，連儂牆，遊行集會，以至街頭抗爭全部都要做番哂</span></span>。咁先對得住所有喺運動中被自殺，被殺，同埋喺拘留所，喺獄中嘅手足。我哋嘅優勢喺懶死唔走嘅人，燒唔完嘅意志，打不死嘅精神，我哋唔係一啲勝算都冇嫁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家中共對香港虎視眈眈，立法會拉布都要佢出聲。再唔抗爭，惡法只會一條接一條：<strong>廿三條，國歌法，辱警罪&hellip;&hellip;</strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港好撚快就有個&quot;市&quot;字喺後面嫁啦。</span></span><br />\n各位巴絲，應承我，堅持落去。<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">終有一日會光復香港，我哋除罩煲底見。</span></span><br />\n<br />\nps1 限聚令暫訂於23號完結<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nps2 好快就五一黃金週啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c157d8ac1c0246852c99a3a84a569c364d110b2","tid":1977011,"uid":191474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:38:34.000Z","msg":"424限聚令正式結束。<br />\n手足們準備好一齊行街街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf9f842c4fbed261f8bae3889a3e9324fed1232","tid":1977011,"uid":207596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:45:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4a49dd441a345a8cf6d65b11fbe19ee6703569eb","tid":1977011,"uid":11156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:46:07.000Z","msg":"已經操好體能準備好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf5447fa6d2ff66e1e16a903c1d14d6f4f2c6ae","tid":1977011,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3904adbc14e5451ac950faf06396645c570b35","tid":1977011,"uid":197866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:57:43.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"b92625624861636cf5dabfc4737154731009b0fa","tid":1977011,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T22:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}